    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0dabdb22-06c8-5100-8df1-583c45ee17a0","html":"<p>Firefox 66 now supports CSS inset property.</p>\n<p>It is defined as a shorthand of top, right, bottom and left.</p>\n<p>The values can be used per the margin property order: top, right, bottom and left.</p>\n<p>For instance .example-a equals .example-b.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.example-a</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">writing-mode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> sideways-rl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">inset</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px 40px 30px 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #c8c800<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.example-b</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">writing-mode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> sideways-rl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #c8c800<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>As I tested, inset has the same effect as top/right/bottom/left when position is absolute, fixed, relative and sticky.</p>\n<p>It doesnâ€™t affect the element when the position is static as well.</p>\n<h3 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inset\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/inset</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-logical/#propdef-inset\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://drafts.csswg.org/css-logical/#propdef-inset</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#search=inset\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://caniuse.com/#search=inset</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-05-26---css-inset-property/css-inset-property","tagSlugs":["/tag/frontend/","/tag/web-development/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-26T12:40:32.169Z","description":"","tags":["Frontend","Web Development"],"title":"CSS Inset Property","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-05-26---css-inset-property/css-inset-property"}},
